data.description: Welcome to Sea Towers, right on the water!  Situated on the beautiful Intercoastal Waterway just moments from picturesque Redington Beach, this freshly painted adorable 2bdrm/2bath condo has everything you need for the laid-back lifestyle you've always dreamed of. Come home to a tranquil waterfront community with breathtaking views, a private fishing dock, tennis courts, a resort-style pool and clubhouse, a putting green, and convenient covered parking just steps from your enviable corner unit. Enter inside through the spacious Florida room that features gorgeous ceramic tile flooring, built-in storage, and plenty of natural light. You'll love the freshly painted open living and dining space that awaits your finishing touch. The enormous and beautifully equipped kitchen offers a unique breakfast bar, tile countertops, and endless cabinetry with new custom hardware. Both light and airy bedrooms have lovely, low-maintenance tile floors, ceiling fans, and pleasingly large closets. Two spotless bathrooms complete the full package of this can't-miss condominium in a luxurious location on the water. A rare and delightful residence like this is sure to sell quickly - call today to schedule your exclusive private tour!
